   <title> The transition-timing-function Property </title>
   <style type="text/css">
      div {
         transition-timing-function: ease;
         transition-property: width, background-color;
         transition-duration: 2s;
         width: 100px;
         height: 100px;
         background: blue;
      }
      div:hover {
         width: 200px;
         background: red;
      }
   </style>
</head>
